# --- Secrets ---
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# --- Node ---
**/node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

# --- Remotion / bundler cache ---
**/remotion/out/
**/remotion/build/
**/.remotion/

# --- Pipeline outputs & logs ---
**/output/
**/logs/
*.log

# --- Generated / downloaded narration & reference media ---
**/input/audio/*
!**/input/audio/.gitkeep
**/input/reference/*
!**/input/reference/.gitkeep

# --- Heavy raw pool (giữ .gitkeep nếu có) ---
**/input/raw_assets/images/*
!**/input/raw_assets/images/.gitkeep
**/input/raw_assets/videos/*
!**/input/raw_assets/videos/.gitkeep
**/input/raw_assets/audio/*
!**/input/raw_assets/audio/.gitkeep

# --- OS / IDE ---
.DS_Store
._*
.idea/
.vscode/
*.code-workspace

# --- Temp ---
*.tmp
*.bak
